Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/Authentication/Sign in/Positive Test Cases/Sign in (Remember Me Selected)
Description:
Valid Email with Remember Me Selected
   - Test Case: Enter a valid email and password, select the "Remember Me" checkbox.
   - Expected Result: User successfully logs in, and the email is pre-filled during the next login attempt.

Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/Authentication/Sign in/Positive Test Cases/Sign in (Uncheck Remember Me)
Description:
Uncheck Remember Me
   - Test Case: Enter a valid email and password, uncheck the "Remember Me" checkbox.
   - Expected Result: User successfully logs in, and the email is not pre-filled during the next login attempt.

Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/Authentication/Sign in/Positive Test Cases/Sign in (Valid Cred)
Description:
1. Valid Email and Password
   - Test Case: Enter a valid email address and correct password.
   - Expected Result: User successfully logs in and is redirected to the home page.
